EN: Handle family conflicts properly to avoid unnecessary harm to the family.

ZH: 年轻人要远离毒品，以免给自己的身体造成损害。
EN: Young people should stay away from drugs to avoid harming their bodies.

ZH: 公司的声誉因员工的不负责任行为而受损害。
EN: The company's reputation has been damaged by the irresponsible behavior of its employees.
